ation of the $0\\nu\\beta\\beta$ backgrounds and a\nmeasurement of the standard double beta decay with neutrinos\n(${2\\nu\\beta\\beta}$). An 8 sigma significance for the ${2\\nu\\beta\\beta}$ signal\nin the NEW detector has been estimated for a 100-day run.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2017 17:19:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
