cts and the kinks in the quasi 1D bands may provide important information\nfor understanding the superconducting state. This work opens up a unique\napproach to revealing the superconducting order parameter in this compound.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2017 20:12:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-26"}
